import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class Timeline extends Component { render() { return (
highlights

Timeline

Senior Product Manager at GEP WorldwideJuly-2021 to Apr-2022

Drive product planning and execution throughout the Product Lifecycle, including gathering and prioritizing product and customer requirements

Deliver platform capabilities with a low-code or no-code implementation

Ensures that the product supports the company's overall strategy and goals and deliver a cloud agnostic Supply Chain and Procurement solution

Product Manager at ServicenowJan-2018 to May 2021

Product Manager for the Now Support ecosystem (previously known as HI) managing mission critical products (Key Products owned: Search on Now Support Portal, Integrations, Instance Management, Service Catalog and Predictive Intelligence)

Build a healthy Product Backlog and prioritize them support changing business needs of the organization

Primary and Higher Education 2003-2015

I have completed my higher secondary education with major subjects as Physics,Chemistry & Maths with 91 merit. During my time at school, I have developed interest in solving complex problems of the fundamental physics which helped me to improve my understanding of any problem and also my mathematical skills to actually solve the problems.

) } }
